{"tid":1908244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波稱不排除開徵銷售稅","createTime":"2020-03-03T06:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T08:55:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8b81c85e3b68ced3191b89881766d1fc87f6c019","tid":1908244,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社３日專訊》財政司司長陳茂波日前接受外電訪問時表示，不排除開徵銷售稅<br />\n，但明白當中具爭議性，亦指樓市方面，由去年８月開始有溫和調整，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未見有快速下跌的風險</span></span></strong><br />\n，認為情況與２００３年及之前不同。<br />\n<br />\n  對於市場關注香港將面對結構性財政赤字，他指這個講法是太早下結論，認為今年香港經濟<br />\n好大機會錄得收縮，但仍有希望因為有幾個月去追，要視乎疫情發展及其後有多大動力去恢復經<br />\n濟，但他認為當疫情過去後，經濟反彈會強勁。"},{"pid":"56617116999e008dde42266bef0ac5a748286774","tid":1908244,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"呢頭話零售銷售數字大跌，嗰個開銷售稅踩多腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3471ca89307e1083ca0de09d43a661e25f9862","tid":1908244,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢頭話零售銷售數字大跌，嗰<span style=\"color: red;\">頭</span>開銷售稅踩多腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"004143fd0b22a6b81e61b9eb17df996eb7f9411b","tid":1908244,"uid":86614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:45:44.000Z","msg":"變購物地獄"},{"pid":"a46e01ddd1f42bdded9d85de089865c62628c776","tid":1908244,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56617116999e008dde42266bef0ac5a748286774","tid":1908244,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"呢頭話零售銷售數字大跌，嗰個開銷售稅踩多腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"零售失業率好似已經係7% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢真係打算用樓價噴射式上升去帶經濟？"},{"pid":"2c200c